{
  "uid": "angular-regression-guard",
  "title": "Angular Regression Guard",
  "description": "Hard CI gate — Angular panel count across the instance MUST be zero. Row turns red otherwise.",
  "tags": ["v12-migration", "platform", "validation", "ci-gate"],
  "schemaVersion": 40,
  "version": 1,
  "editable": false,
  "graphTooltip": 0,
  "refresh": "1m",
  "time": {"from": "now-15m", "to": "now"},
  "timepicker": {},
  "templating": {"list": [
    {"name": "datasource", "type": "datasource", "query": "prometheus", "refresh": 1, "hide": 0, "current": {"text": "Prometheus", "value": "prom"}}
  ]},
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Angular panels on live instance",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "datasource": {"uid": "${datasource}", "type": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [
        {"refId": "A", "expr": "sum(grafana_frontend_angular_panel_count) or vector(0)"}
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": null},
              {"color": "red", "value": 1}
            ]
          },
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]}, "colorMode": "background"}
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Angular plugins loaded",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 0},
      "datasource": {"uid": "${datasource}", "type": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [
        {"refId": "A", "expr": "sum(grafana_plugin_build_info{angular=\"true\"}) or vector(0)"}
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": null},
              {"color": "red", "value": 1}
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]}, "colorMode": "background"}
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 8},
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Guard rule\n\nAny value > 0 on either panel = **CI fails**. Angular was removed in Grafana 12.0; any survivors break the migration contract. Remediation: `migration/20_angular_purge.py` + manual review in `migration/angular-manual-review.md`."
      }
    }
  ]
}
